  contracts/verifier/src/lib.rs adapts the groth16_verifier example. The
  pairing-check structure is taken from that example; this project changed the
  curve from BLS12-381 to BN254 and stores the verification key once at deploy
  time through the constructor instead of passing it on every call. See the
  sourceRef comment at the top of that file.

